openMap4u core API 0.1.0-SNAPSHOT API

Packages 
Package Description
org.openmap4u
The openMap4u API.
org.openmap4u.builder
The core abstract builder for contructing shape, image and text primitive from which the concrete builder implemtations are derived.
org.openmap4u.commons
Contains functionality that is used from more than one package.
org.openmap4u.format
The output format.
org.openmap4u.plugin.builder.chart
Basic charts plugins: Line-, Area-, Bar- and Piechart.
org.openmap4u.plugin.builder.connector  
org.openmap4u.plugin.builder.core
Basic primitive plugins: Line-, Polyline-, Polygon-, Image- and Textprimitive.
org.openmap4u.plugin.builder.symbol
Well known Symbol plugins: Circle-, Cross-, and Rectanglesymbol.
org.openmap4u.plugin.format.graphics2d
Basic raster image output format implementations (GIF, JPEG, PNG).
org.openmap4u.plugin.format.svg
SVG output format plugin implementation.
